Third Department,

March, 1963

(March 13, 1963) In the Matter of New York State Restaurant Association, Inc., Petitioner, v. Board of Standards and Appeals of the State of New York et al., Respondents.

Upon reargument we adhere to our decision transferring the petition and hearing thereon to the Special Term, Albany County. We do not pass upon any jurisdictional or other questions that may be properly raised before the Special Term upon proper application. Concur — Bergan, P. J., Coon, Gibson, Herlihy and Reynolds, JJ.
